name: Freedom Print
description:
Signed limited edition print from a collaboration of work with my friend John Kaye.

All the photographs in this series are original images taken by myself on recent travels then hand painted by John Kaye to alter the final image..

All signed prints are A3 size and printed on high quality 300gsm glossy paper and limited to an edition of 25. 

Prints will be carefully rolled and mailed in a postage tube.

Check out www.jacobdoubleyou.com for more details
